name: Eurydice Among a Blooming Garden
description:
‘Eurydice Among a Blooming Garden' is an interpretation of a mythical character, combining my expressionist modes of expression and my organic lines. Translucent lines are built like networks to structure and unite the background.
Eurydice was a character in Greek mythology and the wife of Orpheus, who tried to raise her from the dead with his enchanting music.
